The Omicron Rocket Project

$OMIR was founded to gather all the people affected by the covid pandemic. Whether the pandemic period has been good or bad for you individually, the fact is that many of us have lost jobs, got mentally broken and down due to the different lockdowns and restrictions. Suicide, and antidepressant medicine has been in the mind of otherwise healthy individuals. Same with loneliness, but we are here to change all of that!

This is why we created Omicron Rocket, to bring covid hit and affected together here in crypto-sphere, and ultimately change the future of people’s lives in a positive way, through SPREADing and multiplying. We’ll affect all crypto channels and media. Together we’ll take $OMIR to outer space.

For such immense goals community is everything, so hop onboard and let’s have FUN!
